{"tid":1229691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"U記仝人，你地到底有撚無人性？返工重要過人權？","createTime":"2019-06-16T04:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T05:57:49.000Z","uid":52658,"like":122,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe84c847536347453eb8ced7b22c7226d6e9079","tid":1229691,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n聽到U記入面有個疑似大粒既人發表偉論<br />\n真係火撚滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&ldquo;反乜撚野送中丫，搞到無人手返工 阻撚住晒&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n你條咁既死奴才 你知唔撚知送中條例一過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你間公司都會撤走啊</span></span><br />\n返工返撚到良知都無撚埋<br />\n人地員工唔要命咁走上街<br />\n你老母條爛鳩經理淨係係度冷嘲熱諷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你又為呢個社會做過d野撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你條友咁撚短視 乜撚都唔識<br />\n祝你成世做U記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>以後唔撚去</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"400ec44affa32b9b4b32e326e2e286ece1925d9a","tid":1229691,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"有腦既唔洗做u記"},{"pid":"d95b05f09c061e2cd9ec067ce79992291b0c962f","tid":1229691,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔去U記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68b9d38f702965c493a46eadfc9f2dd301a9230","tid":1229691,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d95b05f09c061e2cd9ec067ce79992291b0c962f","tid":1229691,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔去U記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"